What is React

    Library for building UI

    Runs on the client, front end framework

Why use it

    Creates structure for the view layer of the application

    Uses reusable components

    Uses JSX dynamic markup

    Interactive UI with virtualDOM avoids reloads

    Very popular

Components

    You can create them as classes or functions

    Have state that determines how the object renders and behaves

Hooks

    Functions that let use the react state

        useState
        useEffect
        useContext
        useReducer
        usRef

Instal React Developer tools in browser

Create React App

    $ npx create-react-app my-app
    
    Creates files and folders

    npm i react-icons

Build folder is where you serve your production

       React dev tools icon will look blue

       Anything in production build 

JSON Server

    Mock server to test the backend
    npm i json-server
    json-server --watch db.json --port5000

React router dom

    npm i 

    use browserourter 

